General.Name: Hemcheck Sweden AB
General.Description: Hemcheck Sweden AB (publ) operates as a medical technology company in Sweden and internationally. The company develops and commercializes Helge, which detects hemolysis in vacuum tubes and blood gas samples. It serves emergency departments in the European Union and the United States. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Solna, Sweden.
